  • IOS_SHOGUN开发文档IOS_SHOGUN_JTO集合

    InfoModel
    IOS_SHOGUN_Component|Intelligence Toolkit
    作者->:Atomic|IOS_SHOGUN_JTO
    Type:JTO集合|Java机制
    Time:2022-4-7|function Level

    Hello developer Welcome to use Toolkit Type IOS_SHOGUN_JTO

    JTO是IOS_SHOGUN开发的一款映射集合在,你可以对它执行一些列的映射键的操作,感官是与Map,Hashmap等映射集合是一致的,映射重复的键将会被覆盖,支持快速序列化,反序列化,你也可以将它添加入IOS_SHOGUN序列表中,支持复杂的JSON对象,快速的转化成JGroovy对象,轻松进行分组管理等(使之快速提取成JTO,MAP,HashMap,Set,Collection等映射键)支持64k以上的文件,以及转变成JSON文件或拷贝,你可以将使用在网络编程中,MAP,HashMap,Set,Collection都支持转变成JTO,我们还加入新型的特色


    JTO is IOS_ A mapping set developed by SHOGUN can be used to perform some mapping key operations on it. It is consistent with Map, Hashmap and other mapping sets. The duplicate keys of mapping will be overwritten. It supports fast serialization and deserialization. You can also add it to IOS_ The SHOGUN sequence table supports complex JSON objects, which can be quickly converted into JGroovy objects (to quickly extract mapping keys such as JTO, MAP, HashMap, Set, Collection, etc.)It supports files of more than 64k and can be converted into JSON files or copied. You can use them in network programming,MAP, HashMap, Set and Collection all support the transformation into JTO, and we also add new features
    无效输入：'&bo'=9QLvAgAAAAADBzg!无效输入：'&rf'=viewer_4"/>
